Class Borrowing

java.lang.Object
LibraryEntities.Borrowing
@Entity public class Borrowing extends Object
Represents a record of a user borrowing a copy of a book.

    • Borrowing

      public Borrowing(Integer id, User user, Copy copy, LocalDate borrowDate)
      Constructs a Borrowing with an existing ID, user, copy, and borrow date.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique ID for this Borrowing.
      user - The user who borrows the copy.
      copy - The specific copy that was borrowed.
      borrowDate - The date the copy was borrowed.
